content: In 1944 a magical device is brought to Bletchley park for study. It is one of the few remaining 'wands' items that can store magical power. During an evening battle between British Soldiers, German Paratoroopers. Mythical creatures and the current wardens the only survivors a re parker who hides the device in Walton Hall by stuffing it into a tree. And a young german  soldier who escapes, but is captured much later as he treis to make the coast.
